snippet.title: Wreckfest - Backwoods Bangers Car Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Expand the World of Wreckfest with 3 more unique vehicles!

Outlaw: This Hot Rod from the 1930s combines american muscle with agility, so it's a great allrounder!

Hornet: This 1980s Euro Coupé stands well against the American muscle cars and is a formidable weapon of choice even for derbies! 

Honey Pot: Make sure to sit REALLY tight whenever this thing goes upside down!

The Backwoods Bangers Car Pack is part of the Season Pass, which is including 20 new cars, 20 special roof decorations and additional car customizations like armor, rims and more. This new content will be released step by step, along with free content updates. Get the Season Pass here:

Steam: http://n.thq.com/IrAv30pvFyk
PlayStation 4: http://n.thq.com/2B0Q30pvFwZ
Xbox One: http://n.thq.com/Ly6Q30pvFxP
